content: Patient #M482-91B (DOB 08/19/1994) presented with chronic pelvic pain and subsequent pelvic floor dysfunction diagnosis. Initial treatment plan included weekly biofeedback sessions at Pine Ridge Health Physio Clinic (555-689-2341) starting 02/15/2024. Provider Dr. Elaine Torres noted potential correlation with patient's ultra-marathon training regimen. Claims submitted under Group ID XQZ-88230 with prior authorization granted for 12 sessions through June 2024.
